        "<span style='font-size: 15px;'><strong>VERSÍCULO: 29</strong></span><br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>TEXTO:</span></strong> Depois deles reparou Zadoque, filho de Imer, defronte da sua casa. Depois dele reparou Semaías, filho de Secanias, guarda da porta oriental.<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ORIGINAL:</span></strong><br>",
        "📜 <strong>Hebraico (BHS):</strong> אַחֲרֵיהֶם הֶחֱזִיק צָדוֹק בֶּן־אִמֵּר נֶגֶד בֵּיתוֹ וְאַחֲרָיו הֶחֱזִיק שְׁמַעְיָה בֶן־שְׁכַנְיָה שֹׁמֵר שַׁעַר הַמִּזְרָח׃<br>",
        "🔤 <strong>Transliteração:</strong> Achareihem hechezik Tzadok ben-Imer negeid beito v'acharav hechezik Sh'ma'yah ben-Sh'chanyah shomer sha'ar hamizrach.<br>",
        "🇬🇷 <strong>Septuaginta (LXX):</strong> μετ᾽ αὐτοὺς ἐπεκρατήσατο Σαδὼκ υἱὸς Ἐμμὴρ κατέναντι τῆς οἰκίας αὐτοῦ· καὶ μετ᾽ αὐτὸν ἐπεκρατήσατο Σαμαίας υἱὸς Σεχενίου, φύλαξ τῆς πύλης τῆς ἀνατολῆς.<br>",
        "🇻🇦 <strong>Vulgata:</strong> post eos aedificavit Sadoc filius Emmer contra domum suam et post eum aedificavit Semeia filius Secheniae custos portae orientalis<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ESTUDO LEXICAL:</span></strong> <em>שֹׁמֵר שַׁעַר הַמִּזְרָח</em> – 'guarda da porta oriental' – guardião da porta do leste.<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>SIMBOLISMO:</span></strong> A porta oriental é importante. O guardião é mencionado. A vigilância é essencial.<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
