        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>TEXTO:</span></strong> Estes, pois, são os filhos de Benjamim: Salu, filho de Mesulão, filho de Joede, filho de Pedaías, filho de Colaías, filho de Maaseias, filho de Itiel, filho de Jesaías.<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ORIGINAL:</span></strong><br>",
        "📜 <strong>Hebraico (BHS):</strong> וְאֵלֶּה בְּנֵי בִנְיָמִן סַלֻּא בֶּן־מְשֻׁלָּם בֶּן־יוֹעֵד בֶּן־פְּדָיָה בֶּן־קוֹלָיָה בֶּן־מַעֲשֵׂיָה בֶּן־אִיתִיאֵל בֶּן־יְשַׁעְיָה׃<br>",
        "🔤 <strong>Transliteração:</strong> V'eleh b'nei Vinyamin Salu ben-M'shulam ben-Yo'ed ben-P'dayah ben-Kolayah ben-Ma'aseyah ben-Iti'el ben-Y'sha'yah.<br>",
        "🇬🇷 <strong>Septuaginta (LXX):</strong> Καὶ οὗτοι υἱοὶ Βενιαμίν· Σηλώμ υἱὸς Μεσουλάμ υἱὸς Ἰωέδ υἱὸς Φαδαΐα υἱὸς Κωλαΐα υἱὸς Μαασίου υἱὸς Ἐθιὴλ υἱὸς Ἰεσίου.<br>",
        "🇻🇦 <strong>Vulgata:</strong> hii autem filii Beniamin Sallu filius Mosollam filius Ioed filius Phadaia filius Colaia filius Maasia filius Ethehel filius Iesaia<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
