        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ORIGINAL:</span></strong><br>",
        "📜 <strong>Hebraico (BHS):</strong> וְאַחֲרָיו גַּבַּי סַלָּי תְּשַׁע מֵאוֹת עֶשְׂרִים וּשְׁמֹנָה׃<br>",
        "🔤 <strong>Transliteração:</strong> V'acharav Gabai Salai tesha me'ot esrim ushmonah.<br>",
