        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>TEXTO:</span></strong> em En-Rimom, em Zorá, em Jarmute,<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ORIGINAL:</span></strong><br>",
        "📜 <strong>Hebraico (BHS):</strong> וּבְעֵין רִמּוֹן וּבְצָרְעָה וּבְיַרְמוּת׃<br>",
        "🔤 <strong>Transliteração:</strong> Uv'Ein Rimmon uv'Tzar'ah uv'Yarmut.<br>",
